Description:
    End-to-end data pipeline that predicts
    loan approval outcomes based on applicant financial risk profiles based on a dataset taken
    of Kaggle.

    Demonstrates an analytics lifecycle relevant credit risk:
        - ETL pipeline ingesting and validating raw financial data
